data.description: Beautiful and timeless Ranch style home with a circle drive in the front, surrounded by mature trees. When you enter this home, you will be overwhelmed with charm and space. The sunken living area and the unique stone fireplace will make you want to cozy up and stay awhile. There are two dining rooms and two living areas, lots of room to spread out. The completely updated kitchen features a large island and custom pantry. The split floor plan includes the master bedroom and two secondary bedrooms on one side, all with plenty of space. On the other side of the house you will find an additional bedroom and bathroom, perfect for guests or a home office. Outside in the backyard, there is a large storage shed and a fenced yard with shade all around. This charming home has all the character and modern updates you can dream of. Come take a look and fall in love, this is truly one of a kind.
